	author = {W. Bulten and K. Kartasalo and Po-Hsuan Cameron Chen and P. Ström and H. Pinckaers and K. Nagpal and Yuannan Cai and David F. Steiner and H. V. van Boven and Robert Vink and C. Hulsbergen–van de Kaa and J. A. van der Laak and M. Amin and A. Evans and T. van der Kwast and Robert Allan and P. Humphrey and H. Grönberg and H. Samaratunga and B. Delahunt and T. Tsuzuki and T. Häkkinen and L. Egevad and Maggie Demkin and Sohier Dane and Fraser Tan and Masi Valkonen and G. Corrado and L. Peng and C. Mermel and P. Ruusuvuori and G. Litjens and M. Eklund},
